                            <li>Get instant help from the community</li>
                            <li>Share tips and tricks</li>
                            <li>Beta testing opportunities</li>
                            <li>Direct access to our team</li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="#" class="community-link">Join Discord</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="community-card">
                    <div class="community-header">
                        <i class="fab fa-reddit"></i>
                        <h3>Reddit Community</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="community-content">
                        <p>Participate in discussions, ask questions, and share your experiences on our subreddit.</p>
                        <ul style="margin: 15px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                            <li>Community-driven support</li>
                            <li>Feature requests and feedback</li>
                            <li>Use case discussions</li>
                            <li>News and updates</li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="#" class="community-link">Visit Subreddit</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="community-card">
                    <div class="community-header">
                        <i class="fab fa-github"></i>
                        <h3>GitHub</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="community-content">
                        <p>Contribute to our open-source projects and report issues on GitHub.</p>
                        <ul style="margin: 15px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                            <li>Report bugs and issues</li>
                            <li>Contribute to documentation</li>
                            <li>Submit feature requests</li>
                            <li>View our roadmap</li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="#" class="community-link">View on GitHub</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="community-card">
                    <div class="community-header">
                        <i class="fab fa-twitter"></i>
                        <h3>Twitter</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="community-content">
                        <p>Follow us on Twitter for the latest news, updates, and quick support.</p>
                        <ul style="margin: 15px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                            <li>Latest feature announcements</li>
                            <li>Quick tips and tutorials</li>
                            <li>Community highlights</li>
                            <li>Support and updates</li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="#" class="community-link">Follow Us</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="discussion-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2>Recent Discussions</h2>
                <p>See what the community is talking about</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="discussion-item">
                <div class="discussion-header">
                    <div class="user-avatar">JD</div>
                    <div>
                        <div><strong>John Doe</strong></div>
                        <div class="discussion-meta">2 hours ago</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <h3 class="discussion-title">Best practices for sharing large video files?</h3>
                <p class="discussion-excerpt">I'm working with 4K video files that are around 50GB each. What's the best way to optimize upload times and ensure reliable delivery to clients?</p>
                <div class="discussion-stats">
                    <span><i class="fas fa-comments"></i> 12 replies</span>
                    <span><i class="fas fa-heart"></i> 8 likes</span>
                    <span><i class="fas fa-eye"></i> 156 views</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="discussion-item">
                <div class="discussion-header">
                    <div class="user-avatar">SM</div>
                    <div>
                        <div><strong>Sarah Mitchell</strong></div>
                        <div class="discussion-meta">5 hours ago</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <h3 class="discussion-title">Feature Request: Bulk upload from cloud storage</h3>
                <p class="discussion-excerpt">Would love to see integration with Google Drive and Dropbox for bulk uploads. Anyone else interested in this feature?</p>
                <div class="discussion-stats">
                    <span><i class="fas fa-comments"></i> 24 replies</span>
                    <span><i class="fas fa-heart"></i> 31 likes</span>
                    <span><i class="fas fa-eye"></i> 289 views</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="discussion-item">
                <div class="discussion-header">
                    <div class="user-avatar">MK</div>
                    <div>
                        <div><strong>Mike Kim</strong></div>
                        <div class="discussion-meta">1 day ago</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <h3 class="discussion-title">API integration success story</h3>
                <p class="discussion-excerpt">Just successfully integrated DropLaa API into our project management tool. Happy to share some code examples if anyone is interested!</p>
                <div class="discussion-stats">
                    <span><i class="fas fa-comments"></i> 18 replies</span>
                    <span><i class="fas fa-heart"></i> 42 likes</span>
                    <span><i class="fas fa-eye"></i> 367 views</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="newsletter-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Stay Connected</h2>
            <p>Subscribe to our newsletter for community highlights, feature updates, and exclusive content</p>
